K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:325a-1: de lta bu'i rgyal srid phun sum tshogs pa shin tu rgya che ba dag kyang rts'a bzhin du bor nas rab tu byung ba'i gzugs dang mtshan ma ston par byed de /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:333b-18: lha mo dri ma med pa'i 'od 'di lung bstan pa yongs su gzung pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:333b-19: sems can thams cad yid dang bar bya ba dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:334a-4: bud med kyi lus las gang du ldog par 'gyur zhes de ltar ma lta zhig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:334a-6: bcom ldan 'das 'o na ji lta bu lags /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:334a-18: sems can thams cad kyi don gyi slad du lha mo dri ma med pa'i 'od kyi lung bstan pa rigs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:334a-19: grong dang bcas par cho ga bzhin du bcom ldan 'das kyis 'dir bshad du gsol /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:334a-20: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:334a-21: lha mo dri ma med pa'i 'od 'di ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:334b-0: nga thabs kyis yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa'i 'og tu lo bdun brgya lon pa @334b na lho phyogs kyi rgyud du yul 'khor mun pa can zhes bya ba zhig 'byung bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:334b-1: yul 'khor chen po de na chu klung nag po bzang zhes bya ba zhig yod pa de'i lho phyogs kyi 'gram na grong khyer dpal yon can des pa zhes bya bar khams kyi rgyal po rgud pa gso ba zhes bya ba'i rigs su 'byung bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:334b-2: khams kyi rgyal po de'i rigs rabs gsum lon pa na rgyal po dpal 'phel zhes bya ba zhig 'byung bar 'gyur te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:334b-7: rgyal po'i pho brang 'khor de 'byor cing rgyas par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:334b-8: de bzhin du mun pa can gyi yul 'khor yang de'i tshe 'byor cing rgyas par 'gyur te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:334b-10: 'bru rnams kyi le tog kyang shin tu phun sum tshogs par 'gyur ro; ;mi rnams kyang bden par smra bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:334b-14: de nas bu mo'i pha rgyal po dpal 'phel gyis bdag nyid kyi bsod nams kyis grong khyer dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:334b-15: yul 'khor 'byor cing rgyas la yul gyi mi rnams shin tu legs par 'khod pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335a-0: 'bru shin tu tshogs par mthong nas bdag nyid kyi bu mo'i ming lo tog 'byor ma zhes yon tan dang @335a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335a-2: de nas rim gyis rgyal po dpal 'phel rang gi bsod nams zad nas 'chi ba'i dus byed par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335a-6: gzhon nu rgyal po nus pa 'ga' yang med kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335a-7: lha mo lo tog 'byor ma 'di nyid rgyal por dbang bskur la rgyal po'i pho brang du de 'dra ba'i gzhon nu 'ga' zhig ming khyer tsam du bzhag ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335a-8: de ltar byas na legs so snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335a-9: de nas lha mo de dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335a-10: rgyal bu gzhon nu de rgyal po byed du bcug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335a-11: pho 'ud ti mo 'ud ti bzhin du snyad btags nas bdag nyid kyi yul du bdag nyid kyis bud med kyi gzugs kyis rgyal srid chen po yongs su spyad de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335a-12: mu stegs can ngan pa'i sde mngon par 'dul bar byed cing dzambu'i gling gi sa gzhi thams cad de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod rten gyi mngon mtshan can du byas nas bkur stir byed /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335a-16: rin po che thams cad kyi gdugs chen po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335a-17: rin po che thams cad kyi ba dan rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335a-18: rin po che thams cad kyi rnam par rgyal ba'i ba dan rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335a-19: spos thams cad kyis bsgos pa'i tsandan gyi phye ma dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335a-27: sel snyan brgya phrag thams cad kyis mchod pa byas nas dzambu'i gling thams cad bskor te dge slong tshul khrims dang ldan pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335b-0: yon tan dang ldan @335b pa rnams la chos gos dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335b-4: yo byad rnams dang ldan par byas te pha rol tu phyin pa bcu'i spyad pa spyod cing rtag tu bslab pa'i gzhi lnga bzung na dbul po la sogs pa khyim bkol gyi sems can thams cad gang dang gang la ci dang cis don du 'gyur ba de dang de la de dang de byin nas 'du shes bcu'i bsdu bas bsdus te spyod par byed cing /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335b-5: sems can bye ba phrag mang bo dag rim bzhin du brtul te sems can de dag gi dge ba'i rtsa ba yongs su smin par shes nas sprin chen po'i mdo 'di la sogs pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis gsungs pa mtshungs pa med pa'i mdo rin po che'i dam pa'i chos bstan pa 'byung bar bya ba'i phyir ci'i thabs kyis kyang mtshungs pa med pa'i sgra sgrog par byed cing /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335b-6: mtshungs pa med pa'i glegs bam bris pa'i snod sangs rgyas kyis gang dang gang du byin gyis brlabs pa'i gnas rnams su 'jog par byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335b-7: de ltar mtshungs pa med pa'i sa bon bskyed nas de'i 'og tu 'chi ba'i dus byed par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335b-8: de'i tshe lha mo lo tog 'byor ma /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335b-11: zab mo shes pa dang ldan pa'i lha mo bud med kyi lus las ldog par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335b-12: sprin chen snying pos gsol pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:335b-14: ci lha mo 'di sems can thams cad kyi dad pa bskyed pa'i slad du cho 'phrul chen po bgyis nas yongs su mya ngan las 'da' bar 'gyur ram /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336a-0: ci lha mo 'di cho 'phrul chen po @336a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336a-1: byed mi nus zhes khyod smra'am /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336a-7: lha mo 'di cho 'phrul chen po ston mi nus so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336a-8: zhes de skad ma zer cig /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336a-12: dzambu'i gling 'di na lha mo 'di la sogs pa dge slong ngam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336a-13: dge slong ma tshul khrims dang ldan par gyur nas yongs su mya ngan las 'da' bar mi 'gyur ba'i sems can de gang yang med de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336a-18: ma 'ongs pa'i sems can bsod nams chung du thams cad kyi dad pa bskyed pa'i phyir mdo 'di las byang chub sems dpa' rnams lung ston par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336a-21: de'i tshe lha mo 'di bud med kyi lus las ldog nas de bzhin gshegs pa 'od dpag med kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'jig rten gyi khams bde ba can du skye ba len par 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336a-22: 'jig rten gyi khams der bde ba nyams su myong nas rim gyis sangs rgyas su 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336a-25: thabs la mkhas pa dang ldan pa'i lha mo 'di yun ji srid cig na sangs rgyas su 'gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336a-26: 'di'i ming yang ji skad ces bgyi bar 'gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336a-27: bcom ldan 'das de'i 'jig rten gyi khams ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-0: bskal pa grangs med pa phrag lnga brgya 'das pa na stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'dir bla na med @336b pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub mngon par 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-1: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rig pa dang zhabs su ldan pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-2: bde bar gshegs pa; 'jig rten mkhyen pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-3: skyes bu 'dul ba'i kha lo sgyur ba bla na med pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-4: lha dang mi rnams kyi ston pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-5: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das gtsang zhing bden pa'i mtshams 'phel bar mdzad pa zhes bya bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-6: 'jig rten gyi khams mi mjed 'di yang 'jig rten gyi khams gtsang ma sbyong ba zhes bya bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-8: gtsang zhing bden pa'i mtshams zhes bya bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-9: 'jig rten gyi khams gtsang ma sbyong ba de 'byor bar 'gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-15: mi mang pos gang bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-16: 'byor cing rgyas par gyur pa de'i tshe dzambu'i gling 'dir grong khyer gtsang ma bsung ldan zhes bya ba zhig 'byung bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-17: grong khyer gtsang ma bsung ldan du mi bye ba brgya stong phrag dgu bcu rtsa brgyad 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-18: dpe med pa'i grong khyer der ra ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-21: 'obs dpe med pa dag 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-22: dag cing nyon mongs zhi bar byed pa'i chu'i klung nag po bzang zhes bya ba ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-23: de'i tshe gtsang ma bzang po zhes bya bar 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:336b-24: 'gram pha rol tshul rol dpe med pa'i shing ljon pa'i kun dga' ra ba nyams dga' ba dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-0: 'jig rten gyi khams gtsang ma sbyong ba de yang @337a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-3: dga' ldan gyi lha rnams kyi longs spyod dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-4: yongs su spyod pa bzhin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-9: gseg ma la sogs pa med par 'gyur zhing mu stegs can gyi ming yang med par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-11: rang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ming yang mi grags par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-12: skyes pa dang bud med dag gi byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun yang 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-14: rang sangs rgyas kyi shes pa'i gtam gyi ming yang med de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-15: theg pa chen po'i mdo'i gtam rgyas par ston par 'gyur ro; ;bdud dang phyir rgol ba bcom pa'i sems can rnams 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-16: dag cing bzod pa chen po'i rnyed pa thob pa dag 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-17: sa gzhi'ang nor bu rin po che thams cad las grub par 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-18: dzambu'i chu bo'i gser gyi me tog dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-19: padma thams cad kyis spras par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-20: de bzhin gshegs pa de'ang tshe dpag tu med par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-21: de bzhin du mi rnams kyi tshe'ang tshad med par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-22: de bzhin gshegs pa de ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337a-23: grong khyer gtsang ma bsung ldan du bzhugs par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337b-0: bcom ldan 'das de'i smon lam gyi khyad par gyis na ma 'ongs pa'i sems can gyi tshogs mang po dag gis de bzhin gshegs pa de'i mtshan thos pa tsam gyis rang gi lus las shi 'phos ma thag tu 'jig rten gyi khams gtsang ma sbyong ba der grong khyer gtsang ma @337b bsung ldan du skye bar 'gyur zhes nga smra'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337b-1: ngan song bzhi'ang de dag gi spyod yul gyi sar mi 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337b-5: bcom ldan 'das 'jig rten gyi khams gtsang ma sbyong ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337b-6: bskal pa gtsang zhing bden pa'i mtshams zhes bya ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337b-7: de bzhin gshegs pa gtsang zhing bden pa'i mtshams 'phel bar mdzad pa zhes bya ba'i yon tan gzung ba smra'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337b-8: de nas 'khor chen po'i nang nas lha dang mi'i tshogs tshad med pas bcom ldan 'das la mchod pa chen po'i las byas te gar byas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337b-9: glu blangs nas bcom ldan 'das de'i byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa la sems bskyed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337b-11: ma 'ongs pa'i sems can bye ma snyed dag lung ston pa sprin chen po'i mdo tsheg dbar brgyad par sbyar ba'i le'u 'bum pa las lung bstan pa'i rgyud yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337b-12: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas sprin chen snying po la sogs pa lha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337b-21: mi ma yin pa rnams yi rang ste bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337b-22: 'phags pa sprin chen po zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo rdzogs so ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337b-23: rgya gar gyi mkhan po su rendra bo dhi dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-064-002:337b-24: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba bandhe ye shes sdes zhus te gtan la phab pa /
